  m_sTitle "Summary"
  m_sTextData "A British platoon must defend CIMIC House against a large-scale Iraqi assault aimed at overrunning and capturing the compound."\
  ""\
  "Can the garrison hold long enough to force the attackers to withdraw?"\
  ""\
